            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1678802263677-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium heat, then add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>basil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and your <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong>, then reduce the heat to low and cook for 5-6 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
