    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Roll out the dough to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling</strong> <strong>pin</strong> (no need to knead!)</p><p>Add the <strong>rolled dough</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two), then spread <strong>half</strong> the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!) and the <strong>stromboli</strong> <strong>filling</strong> all over the dough and top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1678802281420-x200.jpg",
