            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roll the dough over the filling, and continue to roll until you end up with a log shape, seal-side down</p><p>Brush with a little <strong>milk </strong>and sprinkle over your <strong>dried oregano</strong> – this is your <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>veggie</strong> <strong>stromboli</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 22-25 min or until golden and cooked through</p>",
