    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stromboli is golden and cooked through, slice into 3<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>pieces per person</p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>veggie</strong> <strong>stromboli</strong> <strong>slices</strong> with the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>tomato sauce</strong> to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
